        <div class="section-title">Understanding ADD</div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>ADD stands for Attention Deficit Disorder. It's a condition that affects one's ability to focus and maintain attention. While it shares similarities with ADHD (Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder), ADD does not include hyperactive behaviors. It's important to understand and manage ADD through strategies such as structured routines, mindfulness practices, and sometimes medication.</p>
